videoSnippet.description:
Learn the Evans Gambit here! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CUQQ4dym5ZU

Photos by Lenart Ootes
Have a great day :)

Pranav, V (2545) - Praggnanandhaa R (2684)
Julius Baer Challenger Championship (chess24.com) [1] 2022.12.11
C70 Ruy Lopez, Classical defence deferred

1.e4 e5 2.Nf3 Nc6 3.Bb5 a6 4.Ba4 Bc5 5.c3 Nge7 6.d4 exd4 7.cxd4 Bb4+ 8.Bd2 Bxd2+ 9.Nbxd2 d5 10.O-O dxe4 11.Nxe4 O-O 12.h3 Bf5 13.Re1 h6 14.Rc1 Bxe4 15.Rxe4 Qd6 16.a3 Rad8 17.Qc2 Qf6 18.Rce1 Rd6 19.Ne5 b5 20.Bb3 Rxd4 21.Ng4 Qg5 22.Rxd4 Nxd4 23.Qxc7 Ng6 24.Ba2 h5 25.Qc3 Rd8 26.Re4 Nf4 27.Qe3 hxg4 28.Bxf7+ Kh7 29.Kh2 Nf3+ 30.gxf3 gxh3

The Tata Steel Chess India Rapid tournament is a 10-player round-robin taking place from 29 November to 1 December 2022 in the National Library of India in Kolkata.

Players receive 25 minutes for the entire game, plus a 10-second increment starting from move one. Official website: tatasteelchess.in
